TITLE: Apollo and the Muses on Mount Parnassus
DESCRIPTION: Illustration of the nine Muses, goddesses of poetic inspiration and the creative arts, surround the god Apollo, who plays a lira di braccio.
SUBJECTS: Apollo, Muses, Mount Parnassus, Ancient Greece, Drawing
CONTENT: An illustration made with pen and brown ink, brush with brown wash; small, irregular section at right margin added.
